data.title: Zulfikar Ali Bhutto
data.text:
Born: 5-Jan-1928

Birthplace: Larkana, Pakistan

Died: 4-Apr-1979

Location of death: Rawalpindi, Pakistan

Cause of death: Execution

Remains: Buried, Garhi Khuda Baksh, Larkana, Pakistan

Gender: Male

Religion: Muslim

Race or Ethnicity: Asian/Indian

Sexual orientation: Straight

Occupation: Head of State, Activist

Nationality: Pakistan

Executive summary: Head of Pakistan, hanged

Father: Shah Nawaz Bhutto

Wife: Nusrat Isphahani (m. 8-Sep-1951)

Daughter: Benazir Bhutto (b. 21-Jun-1953)

High School: Cathedral High School, Bombay, India

University: University of Southern California

University: BA Political Science, University of California at Berkeley (1950)

University: Oxford University

Prime Minister of Pakistan 1973-77

President of Pakistan 1971-73

Traveled to the USSR 16-Mar-1972

Declared Martial Law Apr-1977

Conspiracy (murder) convicted Sep-1977
